Steps to Reproduce:
1 Click on register
2 Fill the required details
3 Click on join after filling all details
4 Capture the request in the burp
4 Send it to repeater
6 Click on go now
7-You can see the access code in the response body

Impact:
Attacker can create a account with the victim mail id and he can confirm the mail id without the confirmation link.

Note-Use a different browser for recieving the confirmation link. This will help to serach the access token in burp.
